  <summary>9/24/2003--Introduced.
Nuclear Terrorist Threat Reduction Act - Instructs the Secretary of Energy to purchase or otherwise secure excess Russian plutonium and highly enriched uranium. Authorizes appropriations to implement such mandate, including funds for: (1) improving security and accounting for nuclear material in Russia; (2) downsizing and restructuring of Russia's excess nuclear complex; and (3) ensuring transparency in Russia and verifying progress.</summary>
